  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nTruffle spills its guts onto the console when migration script deploys a contract with mismatching number of arguments.\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nCreate contract that takes 3 arguments, yet pass it 4 arguments in the migration script. Run migrate and watch the console just fill up with source code for about 10 minutes.\r\n\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nJust a normal error so that I can move on.\r\n\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nIt fills the entire console with endless source code for about 10 minutes. Unstoppably.\r\n\r\n![Screen Shot 2020-11-03 at 2 49 10 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35537333/98033624-cbdd6d00-1de3-11eb-8df3-6ec6cada3fc9.png)\r\n![Screen Shot 2020-11-03 at 2 50 57 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35537333/98033793-01825600-1de4-11eb-8724-493cb44f4ff3.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: MacOS 10.15.7 \r\n* Ethereum client: Ganache\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): Truffle v5.1.51 (core: 5.1.51)\r\n* node version (`node --version`): 14.12.0\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 6.14.8\r\n",
